STOCK MARKET HACK
You invest $1,000 into a "risky " stock that $1,000 grows to $2,000.
Take the $1,000 profit and put in into a low-risk dividend stock.
use high risk profits to build low-risk wealth.
Keep doing this until your dividend income become a salary.


